{
  "page": "Savior of the City",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Savior of the City</b> is a title granted by King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey Baratheon</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_West\" title=\"Warden of the West\">Warden of the West</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, to honor him for his role in saving <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> from the attack of <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a>.\n</p><p>This is one of the many homages done by the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> to downplay the key role performed by <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> in achieving the victory over Stannis and his followers, as well as whitewashing Tywin's responsibility for the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Sack of King&#39;s Landing\">Sack of King's Landing</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Savior_of_the_City&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_4\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 4\">Chapter 4</a>, Tyrion I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403132606\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 95/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8534/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 409/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 17/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 520/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    8.145      1 -total\n 77.07%    6.277      1 Template:Ref\n 52.34%    4.263      1 Template:Ref/core\n 21.78%    1.774      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:21333-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403132606 and revision id 326868\n -->\n",
